          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679486316360-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the paneer is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely slice a few matchsticks from your <strong>ginger </strong>and finely chop (or grate) the rest</p><p>Slice your <strong>green chilli[es] </strong>in half lengthways</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1679486320827-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1679486320827-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1679486320827-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
